title: Introduction to Oil and Gas Operational Safety
description:
Introduction to Oil and Gas Operational Safety - Wise Global Training (Routledge, 2015).pdf

ISBN 9780415730778

Aligned directly to the NEBOSH syllabus, this book covers the breadth and depth of oil and gas operational safety. This book guides the reader through the principles of how to manage operational risks, carefully conveying a technical subject in a clear, concise manner that readers will find comfortable to read and understand.

Written in full colour by a highly experienced team who have many yearsâ€™ experience within the field, this book is undoubtedly an essential tool to enhance your understanding of operational safety within the oil and gas industry
